headline: Did 28 Years of Dividend Growth Just Reinforce TJX’s (TJX) Investment Case for Stability?
summary: TJX Companies announced a quarterly dividend of $0.425 per share, payable on December 4, 2025, to shareholders on record as of November 13, 2025. This payout extends TJX's record of 28 consecutive years of dividend increases, highlighting management's consistent focus on shareholder returns and signaling confidence in its ongoing business performance.
